        <sponsor name-id="M001139">Mr. Gary G. Miller of California</sponsor> (for himself and <cosponsor name-id="M000087">Mrs. Carolyn B. Maloney of New York</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was referred to the <committee-name committee-id="HBA00">Committee on Financial Services</committee-name>
      </action-desc>
